<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n03046d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03046d">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03046d"> 46(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Oneilles / merdre (Ubu Roi) </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: These two words are taken from Jarry&apos;s <i>Ubu Roi</i>. &lsquo;Oneilles&rsquo; is used several times as a mock version of <i>oreilles</i> <font color="green">[ears]</font>. The play opens with the exclamation, <i>Merdre!</i> - a distortion of <i>Merde!</i> <font color="green">[Shite!]</font> - from P&egrave;re Ubu. </mm> </dd></dl>
